{"segment_id": "shangshu-003-yu-shu-canon-of-shun__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-002", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-003-yu-shu-canon-of-shun", "source_id": "shangshu-003-yu-shu-canon-of-shun__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "尚書·虞書 舜典 [2]", "text_original": "曰若稽古帝舜，曰重華協于帝。濬哲文明，溫恭允塞，玄德升聞，乃命以位。", "text_normalized": "曰若稽古帝舜，曰重華協于帝。濬哲文明，溫恭允塞，玄德升聞，乃命以位。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-003-yu-shu-canon-of-shun__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-003", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-003-yu-shu-canon-of-shun", "source_id": "shangshu-003-yu-shu-canon-of-shun__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "尚書·虞書 舜典 [3]", "text_original": "慎徽五典，五典克從；納于百揆，百揆時敘；賓于四門，四門穆穆；納于大麓，烈風雷雨弗迷。帝曰：「格！汝舜。詢事考言，乃言厎可績，三載。汝陟帝位。」舜讓于德，弗嗣。正月上日，受終于文祖。", "text_normalized": "慎徽五典，五典克從；納于百揆，百揆時敘；賓于四門，四門穆穆；納于大麓，烈風雷雨弗迷。帝曰：「格！汝舜。詢事考言，乃言厎可績，三載。汝陟帝位。」舜讓于德，弗嗣。正月上日，受終于文祖。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-003-yu-shu-canon-of-shun__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-004", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-003-yu-shu-canon-of-shun", "source_id": "shangshu-003-yu-shu-canon-of-shun__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 4, "canonical_ref": "尚書·虞書 舜典 [4]", "text_original": "在璿璣玉衡，以齊七政。肆類于上帝，禋于六宗，望于山川，徧于群神。輯五瑞。既月乃日，覲四岳群牧，班瑞于群后。", "text_normalized": "在璿璣玉衡，以齊七政。肆類于上帝，禋于六宗，望于山川，徧于群神。輯五瑞。既月乃日，覲四岳群牧，班瑞于群后。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-003-yu-shu-canon-of-shun__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-005", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-003-yu-shu-canon-of-shun", "source_id": "shangshu-003-yu-shu-canon-of-shun__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 5, "canonical_ref": "尚書·虞書 舜典 [5]", "text_original": "歲二月，東巡守，至于岱宗，柴。望秩于山川，肆覲東后。協時月正日，同律度量衡。修五禮、五玉、三帛、二生、一死贄。如五器，卒乃復。五月南巡守，至于南岳，如岱禮。八月西巡守，至于西岳，如初。十有一月朔巡守，至于北岳，如西禮。歸，格于藝祖，用特。五載一巡守，群后四朝。敷奏以言，明試以功，車服以庸。", "text_normalized": "歲二月，東巡守，至于岱宗，柴。望秩于山川，肆覲東后。協時月正日，同律度量衡。修五禮、五玉、三帛、二生、一死贄。如五器，卒乃復。五月南巡守，至于南岳，如岱禮。八月西巡守，至于西岳，如初。十有一月朔巡守，至于北岳，如西禮。歸，格于藝祖，用特。五載一巡守，群后四朝。敷奏以言，明試以功，車服以庸。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-003-yu-shu-canon-of-shun__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-006", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-003-yu-shu-canon-of-shun", "source_id": "shangshu-003-yu-shu-canon-of-shun__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 6, "canonical_ref": "尚書·虞書 舜典 [6]", "text_original": "肇十有二州，封十有二山，濬川。", "text_normalized": "肇十有二州，封十有二山，濬川。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-003-yu-shu-canon-of-shun__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-007", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-003-yu-shu-canon-of-shun", "source_id": "shangshu-003-yu-shu-canon-of-shun__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 7, "canonical_ref": "尚書·虞書 舜典 [7]", "text_original": "象以典刑，流宥五刑，鞭作官刑，扑作教刑，金作贖刑。眚災肆赦，怙終賊刑。欽哉，欽哉，惟刑之恤哉！流共工于幽洲，放驩兜于崇山，竄三苗于三危，殛鯀于羽山，四罪而天下咸服。", "text_normalized": "象以典刑，流宥五刑，鞭作官刑，扑作教刑，金作贖刑。眚災肆赦，怙終賊刑。欽哉，欽哉，惟刑之恤哉！流共工于幽洲，放驩兜于崇山，竄三苗于三危，殛鯀于羽山，四罪而天下咸服。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-003-yu-shu-canon-of-shun__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-008", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-003-yu-shu-canon-of-shun", "source_id": "shangshu-003-yu-shu-canon-of-shun__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 8, "canonical_ref": "尚書·虞書 舜典 [8]", "text_original": "二十有八載，帝乃殂落。百姓如喪考妣，三載，四海遏密八音。", "text_normalized": "二十有八載，帝乃殂落。百姓如喪考妣，三載，四海遏密八音。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-003-yu-shu-canon-of-shun__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-009", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-003-yu-shu-canon-of-shun", "source_id": "shangshu-003-yu-shu-canon-of-shun__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 9, "canonical_ref": "尚書·虞書 舜典 [9]", "text_original": "月正元日，舜格于文祖，詢于四岳，闢四門，明四目，達四聰。「咨，十有二牧！」曰，「食哉惟時！柔遠能邇，惇德允元，而難任人，蠻夷率服。」", "text_normalized": "月正元日，舜格于文祖，詢于四岳，闢四門，明四目，達四聰。「咨，十有二牧！」曰，「食哉惟時！柔遠能邇，惇德允元，而難任人，蠻夷率服。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-003-yu-shu-canon-of-shun__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-010", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-003-yu-shu-canon-of-shun", "source_id": "shangshu-003-yu-shu-canon-of-shun__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 10, "canonical_ref": "尚書·虞書 舜典 [10]", "text_original": "舜曰：「咨，四岳！有能奮庸熙帝之載，使宅百揆亮采，惠疇？」僉曰：「伯禹作司空。」帝曰：「俞，咨！禹，汝平水土，惟時懋哉！」禹拜稽首，讓于稷、契暨皋陶。帝曰：「俞，汝往哉！」", "text_normalized": "舜曰：「咨，四岳！有能奮庸熙帝之載，使宅百揆亮采，惠疇？」僉曰：「伯禹作司空。」帝曰：「俞，咨！禹，汝平水土，惟時懋哉！」禹拜稽首，讓于稷、契暨皋陶。帝曰：「俞，汝往哉！」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-003-yu-shu-canon-of-shun__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-011", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-003-yu-shu-canon-of-shun", "source_id": "shangshu-003-yu-shu-canon-of-shun__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 11, "canonical_ref": "尚書·虞書 舜典 [11]", "text_original": "帝曰：「棄，黎民阻飢，汝后稷，播時百穀。」", "text_normalized": "帝曰：「棄，黎民阻飢，汝后稷，播時百穀。」", "notes": ""}
