{"segment_id": "shangshu-003-yu-shu-canon-of-shun__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-013", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-003-yu-shu-canon-of-shun", "source_id": "shangshu-003-yu-shu-canon-of-shun__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 13, "canonical_ref": "尚書·虞書 舜典 [13]", "text_original": "帝曰：「皋陶，蠻夷猾夏，寇賊姦宄。汝作士，五刑有服，五服三就。五流有宅，五宅三居。惟明克允！」", "text_normalized": "帝曰：「皋陶，蠻夷猾夏，寇賊姦宄。汝作士，五刑有服，五服三就。五流有宅，五宅三居。惟明克允！」", "notes": ""}
